c: 24
v: 62
t: "AmakholwaokwenenengabobakholwakuAllâhnoMthunywa waKhe kuphela, naxa bedibana naye ngemicimbi eyinzuzo kuye nakubo, bangahambi bengacelanga imvume kuye kuqala. Inene, abo bacela imvume yakho, wena (Muhammad) abo ngabo bakholwa (ngokwenene) kuAllâh nakuMthunywa waKhe. Ke kaloku xa becela imvume kuwe yemicimbi eyiyeyabo, banike. Nika imvume kulowo uthande ukumnika kubo uze ubacelele itarhu kuAllâh. Inene uAllâh nguMxoleli yaye Unenceba"